gents, with native support for OpenAI, LangChain, CrewAI, AutoGen, and more, featuring authenticated tool calls, function calling, real-time execution, and a unified SDK for TypeScript and Python.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"76fb72b997dbfa7d\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"pyshine.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1392e3b7301f5a03\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTools & Toolkits | ComposioHQ/composio | DeepWiki\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1392e3b7301f5a03\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://deepwiki.com/ComposioHQ/composio/2.1-tools-and-toolkits\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"32eacbf3ac277f4c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTools & Toolkits Relevant source files This document defines the fundamental concepts of Tools and Toolkits in Composio : what they are, how they're organized, how to discover them, and how their schemas work. This covers the conceptual model and data structures for the 1000+ integrations in the Composio catalog.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"32eacbf3ac277f4c\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"deepwiki.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"41d79fc6dc44eb67\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nComposio SDK - AI Agent Integration Toolkit | EveryDev.ai\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"41d79fc6dc44eb67\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.everydev.ai/tools/composio-sdk\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a7c59ab97ab6bae9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAbout Composio SDK Composio SDK is an open-source toolkit that provides AI agents with seamless access to 1000+ integrations including Gmail, Slack, GitHub, and Notion. It supports both Python and TypeScript, offering provider packages for all major AI frameworks such as OpenAI, Anthropic, LangChain, LlamaIndex, CrewAI, AutoGen, and more.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a7c59a