{"type":"message","id":"00fda005","parentId":"7c3d7ee0","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:09:10.856Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_8OCafp1azHcgj2Gqfz5M8329","toolName":"composio__COMPOSIO_MANAGE_CONNECTIONS","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"data\":{\"message\":\"All connections have been initiated and are pending completion\",\"results\":{\"gmail\":{\"toolkit\":\"gmail\",\"status\":\"initiated\",\"redirect_url\":\"https://connect.composio.dev/link/lk_uSyDHZVjEiLv\",\"instruction\":\"Action required: Share the following authentication link with the user to complete setup for 'gmail'.\\n\\nAuthentication Link (render clickable):\\nhttps://connect.composio.dev/link/lk_uSyDHZVjEiLv\\n\\nWhat happens next:\\n1) User opens the link in their browser. They will see a Composio branded authentication UI.\\n2) For OAuth: user authorizes with the provider.\\n3) For API/Token auth: User enters the required credentials in the form.\\n4) The connection becomes Active automatically once completed.\\n\\nImportant Notes:\\n- DO NOT execute any gmail tools until an Active connection is confirmed.\\n- After sharing the link, call COMPOSIO_WAIT_FOR_CONNECTIONS with toolkits: [\\\"gmail\\\"] to poll until the connection becomes active.\\n- Render as clickable link: [Connect gmail](https://connect.composio.dev/link/lk_uSyDHZVjEiLv).\\n- The above link expires in 10 minutes.\\n\",\"accounts\":[{\"id\":\"gmail_fret-ayless\",\"status\":\"initiated\",\"is_default\":true,\"account_type\":\"PRIVATE\"}]},\"googledrive\":{\"toolkit\":\"googledrive\",\"status\":\"initiated\",\"redirect_url\":\"https://connect.composio.dev/link/lk_C9qnNNNs_Nom\",\"instruction\":\"Action required: Share the following authentication link with the user to complete setup for 'googledrive'.\\n\\nAuthentication Link (render clickable):\\nhttps://connect.composio.dev/link/lk_C9qnNNNs_Nom\\n\\nWhat happens next:\\n1) User opens the link in their browser. They will see a Composio branded authentication 