dd \"group:messaging\", or      │\n│    switch the agent to a profile that includes messaging tools.          │\n│                                                                          │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  State integrity ────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                      │\n│  - Found 14 orphan transcript files in                               │\n│    ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions.                                 │\n│    These .jsonl files are no longer referenced by sessions.json, so  │\n│    they are not part of any active session history.                  │\n│    Doctor can archive them safely by renaming each file to           │\n│    *.deleted.<timestamp>.                                            │\n│    Examples: 0700aa3e-27f6-4a48-adc6-3c896d6651c9.jsonl,             │\n│    11258e58-4445-49fd-ac3e-0f090732c336.jsonl,                       │\n│    1a1a114e-9f22-4605-84b4-764b9ed5e6a0.jsonl, and 11 more           │\n│                                                                      │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Session locks ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                              │\n│  - Found 1 session lock file.                                                │\n│  - ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/634ee033-149b-400b-a3ec-f2c11f19aa74.js  │\n│  onl.lock                                                                    │\n│    pid=236366 (alive) age=12s stale=no                                       │\n│                                                                              │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Security ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                        │\n│  - WARNING: openclaw.json contains plaintext secret-bearing config     │\n│    fields.                                                             │\n│    Paths: gateway.auth.token                                           │\n│    Agents or workspace tools that can read config files may see these  │\n│    API keys/tokens.                                                    │\n│    Migrate them to SecretRefs with openclaw secrets configure or       │\n│    openclaw secrets apply, then verify with openclaw secrets audit     │\n│    --check.                                                            │\n│  - Run: openclaw security audit --deep                                 │\n│                                                                        │\n├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Skills status ────────────╮\n│                            │\n│  Eligible: 16              │\n│  Missing requirements: 42  │\n│  Blocked by allowlist: 0   │\n│                            │\n├────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Plugins ──────╮\n│                │\n│  Loaded: 68    │\n│  Imported: 0   │\n│  Disabled: 27  │\n│  Errors: 0     │\n│                │\n├────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Skills ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                          │\n│  Some skills are allowed for this agent but are not usable in the        │\n│  current runtime environment.                                            │\n│  - 1password: bins: op                                                   │\n│    install option: Install 1Password CLI (brew)                          │\n│  - apple-notes: bins: memo; os: darwin                                   │\n│  - apple-reminders: bins: remindctl; os: darwin                          │\n│  - bear-notes: bins: grizzly; os: darwin                                 │\n│  - blogwatcher: bins: blogwatcher                                        │\n│    install option: Install blogwatcher (go)                              │\n│  - blucli: bins: blu                                                     │\n│    install option: Install blucli (go)                                   │\n│  - camsnap: bins: camsnap                                                │\n│    install option: Install camsnap (brew)                                │\n│  - clawhub: bins: clawhub                                                │\n│    install option: Install clawhub (npm)                                 │\n│  - coding-agent: any bins: claude, codex, opencode; config:              │\n│    skills.entries.coding-agent.enabled                                   │\n│    install option: Install @anthropic-ai/claude-code (npm)               │\n│  - discord: config: channels.discord.token                               │\n│  - eightctl: bins: eightctl                                              │\n│    install option: Install eightctl (go)                                 │\n│  - gemini: bins: gemini                                                  │\n│    install option: Install Gemini CLI (brew)                             │\n│  - gh-issues: bins: gh                                                   │\n│    install option: Install GitHub CLI (brew)                             │\n│  - gifgrep: bins: gifgrep                                                │\n│    install option: Install gifgrep (go)                                  │\n│  - github: bins: gh                                                      │\n│    install option: Install GitHub CLI (brew)                             │\n│  - gog: bins: gog                                                        │\n│    install option: Install gog (brew)                                    │\n│  - goplaces: bins: goplaces; env: GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY                  │\n│    install option: Install goplaces (brew)                               │\n│  - himalaya: bins: himalaya                                              │\n│    install option: Install Himalaya (brew)                               │\n│  - imsg: bins: imsg; os: darwin                                          │\n│  - model-usage: bins: codexbar; os: darwin                               │\n│  - nano-pdf: bins: nano-pdf                                              │\n│    install option: Install nano-pdf (uv)                                 │\n│  - obsidian: bins: obsidian                                              │\n│  - openai-whisper: bins: whisper                                         │\n│    install option: Install OpenAI Whisper (brew)                         │\n│  - openai-whisper-api: env: OPENAI_API_KEY                               │\n│    install option: Install curl (brew)                                   │\n│  - openhue: bins: openhue                                                │\n│    install option: Install OpenHue CLI (brew)                            │\n│  - oracle: bins: oracle                                                  │\n│    install option: Install @steipete/oracle (npm)                        │\n│  - ordercli: bins: ordercli                                              │\n│    install option: Install ordercli (go)                                 │\n│  - peekaboo: bins: peekaboo; os: darwin                                  │\n│  - sag: bins: sag; env: ELEVENLABS_API_KEY                               │\n│    install option: Install sag (brew)                                    │\n│  - session-logs: bins: rg                                                │\n│    install option: Install jq (brew)                                     │\n│  - sherpa-onnx-tts: env: SHERPA_ONNX_RUNTIME_DIR, SHERPA_ONNX_MODEL_DIR  │\n│    install option: Download sherpa-onnx runtime (Linux x64)              │\n│    install option: Download Piper en_US lessac (high)                    │\n│  - slack: config: channels.slack                                         │\n│  - songsee: bins: songsee                                                │\n│    install option: Install songsee (brew)                                │\n│  - sonoscli: bins: sonos                                                 │\n│    install option: Install sonoscli (go)                                 │\n│  - spotify-player: any bins: spogo, spotify_player                       │\n│    install option: Install spogo (brew)                                  │\n│  - summarize: bins: summarize                                            │\n│    install option: Install summarize (brew)                              │\n│  - things-mac: bins: things; os: darwin                                  │\n│  - trello: env: TRELLO_API_KEY, TRELLO_TOKEN                             │\n│    install option: Install jq (brew)                                     │\n│  - video-frames: bins: ffmpeg                                            │\n│    install option: Install ffmpeg (brew)                                 │\n│  - voice-call: config: plugins.entries.voice-call.enabled                │\n│  - wacli: bins: wacli                                                    │\n│    install option: Install wacli (go)                                    │\n│  - xurl: bins: xurl                                                      │\n│    install option: Install xurl (brew)                                   │\n│  Disable unused skills: openclaw doctor --fix                            │\n│  Inspect details: openclaw skills check --agent <id> or openclaw skills  │\n│  info <name> --agent <id>                                                │\n│                                                                          │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n\nProcess exited with signal SIGKILL."}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","sessionId","exitCod